sentence: We have acted as special counsel to Regency Energy Partners LP, a Delaware limited partnership (the Partnership), Regency Energy Finance Corp., a Delaware corporation (Regency Finance and, together with the Partnership, the Issuers), and the entities listed on Schedule I hereto (collectively, the Guarantors), in connection with the filing on the date hereof with the Securities and Exchange Commission (the Commission) of Post-Effective Amendment No. 1 (the Amendment) to the registration statement on Form S-3 (File No. 333-169901) (the Registration Statement) under the Securities Act of 1933, as amended (the Act).
